  11 Aug 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.8.0.ebuild:
  stable x86, bug 280484

*bwidget-1.8.0 (20 Apr 2007)

  20 Apr 2007; Steve Arnold <nerdboy@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.7.0.ebuild,
  +bwidget-1.8.0.ebuild:
  Updated to current version required by setools (the latter won't build
  the apol gui against earlier versions).  Also fixed lib path in 1.7.0

  22 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  21 Apr 2005; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.7.0.ebuild:
  stable on amd64

  02 Apr 2005; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Stable on SPARC.

  31 Dec 2004; Ciaran McCreesh <ciaranm@gentoo.org> :
  Change encoding to UTF-8 for GLEP 31 compliance

  03 Jun 2004; Bryan Østergaard <kloeri@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha.

  14 Apr 2004; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.4.1.ebuild:
  Added IUSE=

*bwidget-1.7.0 (04 Apr 2004)

  04 Apr 2004; Chris Aniszczyk <zx@gentoo.org> :
  Version bump. Added metadata.xml.

  14 Jan 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.4.1.ebuild:
  add ~alpha

  15 Dec 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.4.1.ebuild:
  Added ~sparc keyword to fix broken dependencies in app-sci/lard.

  13 Feb 2003; Mark Guertin <gerk@gentoo.org> bwidget-1.4.1.ebuild :
  set ppc in keywords

*bwidget-1.4.1 (14 Aug 2002)
